  <metadata>
    <name>ATH-L3 — Mani Peninsula Weekend Loop</name>
    <desc>Deploy from ATH and ride into the Mani Peninsula. Hit Corinth Canal Viewpoint — 75m and Kalamata. Loop back to ATH over a packed 2–3 day weekend escape. No highways, just curves and elevation.</desc>
